  <section class="mt-10 space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Accessibility</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      StatCard components are designed with comprehensive accessibility features
      and WCAG AAA compliance. All text maintains 9:1 contrast ratios and
      adjusts automatically for high contrast mode and dark themes.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      Trend indicators use both color and directional arrows to convey
      information, ensuring accessibility for users with color vision
      differences. Screen readers receive detailed information about trends and
      context through ARIA labels.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-200">
      The component respects user preferences for reduced motion and provides
      semantic structure through proper HTML elements and ARIA roles. Focus
      management is handled automatically for interactive content.
    </p>
